You remind me of a girl
in a Dutch painting.

39:28.490 --> 39:30.200
You have a strange face.

39:30.400 --> 39:32.370
It's plain, but...

39:33.320 --> 39:34.850
...fascinating.

39:35.050 --> 39:36.980
It has a beautiful...

39:38.460 --> 39:40.160
...turbulence.

39:40.360 --> 39:41.980
I love it.

39:46.070 --> 39:48.690
I bet you have
brilliant dreams.

39:49.730 --> 39:51.960
I bet you dream
of other worlds.

39:52.160 --> 39:53.960
[chuckles]

39:54.160 --> 39:57.090
Maybe you'll dream of me
and my morning remorse,

39:57.290 --> 39:59.310
which is certain.

39:59.510 --> 40:01.580
I shouldn't drink,

40:01.780 --> 40:03.880
- but I do.
- [keys jingling]

40:04.080 --> 40:05.530
[both chuckle]

40:07.570 --> 40:09.180
Thank you.

40:15.540 --> 40:17.580
♪

40:20.670 --> 40:22.640
[car door opens]

40:22.840 --> 40:24.200
