41:28.390 --> 41:30.440
[coughing]

41:35.180 --> 41:37.230
[groaning]

41:52.550 --> 41:54.460
♪

41:55.420 --> 41:57.300
[grunting]

41:57.500 --> 41:59.470
[dog barking in distance]

42:00.470 --> 42:02.920
[retching]

42:03.120 --> 42:05.080
[groaning]

42:20.010 --> 42:21.970
[rattling]

42:32.460 --> 42:34.510
Dad. Dad.

42:34.710 --> 42:36.420
Dad, can you let me in?

42:37.590 --> 42:39.070
Shit.

42:43.900 --> 42:45.910
[grunting]

42:46.860 --> 42:50.430
[coughs]

43:00.750 --> 43:02.500
Hey, Dad!

43:02.700 --> 43:04.850
Can I have the keys?

43:05.050 --> 43:06.940
Can I please have the keys?

43:07.140 --> 43:09.550
- [thuds]
- No, you may not have the keys.

43:09.750 --> 43:11.420
Not until you read that book
from cover to cover.

43:11.620 --> 43:13.590
I want to hear every word.

43:19.850 --> 43:21.590
Where'd you put the keys?

43:24.210 --> 43:25.820
Make yourself comfortable,
Eileen.

43:26.020 --> 43:28.700
You're not going anywhere
till you read the last word.

43:28.900 --> 43:31.080
Dad, this is ridiculous.
I need to go to work.

43:32.040 --> 43:33.220
Out all night.

43:33.420 --> 43:34.660
Nearly crashed the car.

43:34.860 --> 43:36.920
Sleeping in your own sick,

43:37.120 --> 43:39.060
and now you're worried
about getting to work on time?

43:39.250 --> 43:41.090
I can hardly look at you,
I'm so ashamed.

43:42.400 --> 43:45.710
Oliver Twist would be grateful
for this home,

43:45.910 --> 43:47.590
but you, Eileen,

43:47.790 --> 43:49.110
you're trash, Eileen,
just trash.

43:49.310 --> 43:51.590
All I did was go out
with a girl from work.

43:51.790 --> 43:52.940
You went out
with a girl from work?

43:53.140 --> 43:54.370
Do I look like
I was born yesterday?

43:54.570 --> 43:56.070
Who is he? Huh?

43:56.270 --> 43:58.250
Who is this boy?
I just want to know who he is

43:58.450 --> 44:00.210
before you get knocked up
and sell your soul to Satan.

44:00.410 --> 44:02.640
Can you just give me the keys?!

44:02.840 --> 44:04.340
Please! I'll be late!

44:04.540 --> 44:06.430
You're not going anywhere
dressed like that.

44:06.630 --> 44:08.780
I mean, really, Eileen,
how dare you?

44:08.980 --> 44:11.610
That's the dress your mother
wore to my father's funeral.

44:11.810 --> 44:13.790
You got no respect for anyone.

44:13.990 --> 44:15.270
Get changed.

44:15.460 --> 44:17.700
I don't want anyone
seeing you in that getup.

44:17.900 --> 44:19.260
They'll think I'm dead.

44:21.440 --> 44:23.010
- [car door closes]
- [coughs]

44:23.210 --> 44:25.490
[wind blowing]

44:25.690 --> 44:27.310
Ah. Miss Dunlop?

44:28.620 --> 44:29.710
May I, um, may I have a word?

44:29.910 --> 44:32.060
Oh, Jesus.

44:32.260 --> 44:33.590
It's about your father.

44:33.790 --> 44:35.760
Him? Go talk to him.
He's inside.

44:35.960 --> 44:37.110
It's about his gun.

44:37.310 --> 44:38.380
EILEEN:
This oughta be good.

44:38.570 --> 44:40.550
Pray tell, Buck.

44:40.750 --> 44:41.940
Uh, yesterday,

44:42.140 --> 44:43.950
we got several complaints
from neighbors,

44:44.150 --> 44:45.640
from Miss Connie
down at the school,

44:45.840 --> 44:47.820
that, uh, Chief Dunlop

44:48.020 --> 44:51.480
was sitting
in that north-facing window

44:51.670 --> 44:54.040
and, uh, pointing his weapon

44:54.240 --> 44:55.520
at children walking home
from school.

44:55.720 --> 44:57.310
[sighs]

44:57.510 --> 44:59.830
He has agreed to relinquish
the property into your care.

45:00.030 --> 45:02.180
As long as you promise
not to use it on him.

45:02.380 --> 45:03.700
His words. [chuckles]

45:04.650 --> 45:05.660
May I come in?

45:05.860 --> 45:07.060
♪

45:07.260 --> 45:09.970
Want to hang it on me
like an ornament?

45:10.170 --> 45:11.230
BUCK:
Aw. [chuckles]

45:11.430 --> 45:13.110
I'm sure that Miss Dunlop

45:13.310 --> 45:15.240
will take excellent care
of the weapon, sir.

45:15.440 --> 45:18.670
As she does with all things,
Buck, as you can see.

45:21.580 --> 45:22.940
[body thuds]

45:23.140 --> 45:24.730
["Good Morning Blues"
by Dee Dee Ford playing]

45:24.930 --> 45:25.860
[engine revs]

45:26.060 --> 45:28.690
[coughs]

45:28.890 --> 45:29.690
[car horn honks]

45:29.890 --> 45:31.690
